Actions.Text: AMEND (T) AND RECOMMIT TO WAYS AND MEANS

Title: Relates to exempting from tax a portion of global intangible low-taxed income
Summary: Exempts from tax a portion of global intangible low-taxed income.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the tax law and the administrative code of the city of New York, in relation to the definitions of the terms "CFC income" and "entire net income"
